document_data.name: ''Staff of Travaran''
document_data.mainbody: The '''''Staff of Travaran''''' was an ancient unique [[magic item]] from the island of [[Evermeet]].
document_data.Description: A {{SI|6|ft|long=yes}} piece of ashwood composed the body of the [[staff]]. A [[silver]] [[horse]] end was found at the end.
document_data.Powers: This powerful item combined all of the powers of a ''[[staff of the magi]]'' with a ''[[staff of wizardry]]''.
